      <title>中国银行大幅下调贷款利率以提振疲弱经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/chinese-banks-slash-key-lending-rates-to-bolster-ailing-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为旨在恢复经济增长和阻止房地产市场崩溃的一系列措施之一，中国央行在 9 月底降低了基准贷款利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/chinese-banks-slash-key-lending-rates-to-bolster-ailing-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
